title: Nestled in a green lakeside setting!
posting_body: Text 8282A to my cell for more info!
Welcome to The Estates Apartments in Austin.
This unique apartment community is nestled in a green, lakeside setting that is sure to provide the ultimate in comfort, relaxation, and recreation.
We offer a wide selection of one and two bedroom apartments for rent with the finest features.
Between this sought after location and the variety of amenities we provide, you are sure to feel right at home.
You will not be short on options with five different floor plan options.
Relax in your living room or on your patio and take in the available lake views.
Residents also have access to the lakeside running and walking trail.
When you move into your beautiful home you will enjoy all of the nearby shopping and dining conveniences.
You name it, we have it here at The Estates.
Call now for availability information and schedule your personal tour today!
Take your pick of your new home.
Choose from our open-area, one-bedroom layouts, or our two-bedroom homes tailored with space for you to grow into.
